Label.Text: This allows you to define any additional Business Number Types to be entered against vendors in the system, the expected format, and if this should be the default type for new vendors.

Information.Text: Represent numbers using "0" as a placeholder, and <space> for spaces. No other elements are supported. Leave blank if there is no strict format.

If selected, new vendors will use the selected business number type on creation. Vendors created through integration will use the Business Number Type provided through integration, if any.
Only one type can be the default.
This will allow a user to validate the business number against a registrar. The functionality to support this has to be coded, if supported then the function will be checked automatically.
